```class Solution {
    public int countNumbers(String l, String r, int b) {
        int MOD = 1000000007;
        int count = 0;
        for (int i = Integer.parseInt(l); i <= Integer.parseInt(r); i++) {
            String s = Integer.toString(i, b);
            boolean nonDecreasing = true;
            for (int j = 1; j < s.length(); j++) {
                if (s.charAt(j - 1) > s.charAt(j)) {
                    nonDecreasing = false;
                    break;
                }
            }
            if (nonDecreasing) {
                count = (count + 1) % MOD;
            }
        }
        return count;
    }
}```
